of content check discount nexeon medsystems inc nexeon is a privately held medical device company based in the us it develops and commercializes therapies and devices for the treatment of cardiovascular diseases the company focuses on interventional cardiology related devices and technologies its products include protex coronary stent system and citation peripheral stent system nexeons products are based upon inversion point technology it also offers nanotechnology based transcatheter designs embolic protection systems local drugbiologic delivery systems based upon frontier technologies the company has nexeon medsystems innovation center present in california the us its partners include unidym inc and surmodics inc nexeon is headquartered in charleston west virginia the us this report is a source for data analysis and actionable intelligence on the nexeon medsystems inc portfolio of pipeline products the report provides detailed analysis on each pipeline product with information on the indication the development stage trial phase product milestones pipeline territory estimated approval date and estimated launch date each pipeline product is profiled to cover information on product description function technology indication and application the report is also supplemented with a detailed company profile and information on clinical trials wherever applicable this report is built using data and information sourced from proprietary databases primary and secondary research and inhouse analysis by globaldatas team of industry experts scope detailed company profile with information on business description key company facts major products and services key competitors key employees locations and subsidiaries and recent developments detailed coverage on all the pipeline products by equipment type by therapy area by development stage and by trial phase information on product milestones and pipeline territory for each product the estimated approval date and estimated launch date